{"word":"H7782 - שֹׁופָר - shôwphâr - sho-far' - Cornet - கொம்பு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>שֹׁופָר"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shôwphâr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>sho-far'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Cornet / கொம்பு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"எக்காளம், கொம்பு - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a horn, a ram's horn"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/H8231 - שָׁפַר - shâphar - shaw-far'/8231\">H8231</a> in the original sense of <i>incising</i>; a <i>cornet</i> (as giving a <i>clear</i> sound) or curved horn: - cornet, trumpet."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7782 - שֹׁופָר - shôwphâr - sho-far'/7782\">H7782</a>, <a href=\"#/H8208 - שָׁפִיר - Shâphîyr - shaf-eer'/8208\">H8208</a>, <a href=\"#/H8231 - שָׁפַר - shâphar - shaw-far'/8231\">H8231</a>, <a href=\"#/H8233 - שֶׁפֶר - shepher - sheh'-fer/8233\">H8233</a>, <a href=\"#/H8234 - שֶׁפֶר - Shepher - sheh'-fer/8234\">H8234</a>, <a href=\"#/H8235 - שִׁפְרָה - shiphrâh - shif-raw'/8235\">H8235</a>, <a href=\"#/H8236 - שִׁפְרָה - Shiphrâh - shif-raw'/8236\">H8236</a>, <a href=\"#/H8237 - שַׁפְרוּר - shaphrûwr - shaf-roor'/8237\">H8237</a>, <a href=\"#/H8240 - שָׁפָת - shâphâth - shaw-fawth'/8240\">H8240</a>"}]}